{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we climbed up when we heard a shooting in the morning, without warning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father pulled up the ladder, and we were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't sit up, because it was not too high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to lay there flat and wait.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we heard much shooting going on in town, frightened, not knowing what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my younger sister Rosa, she had a stomachache.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was nothing that could be done, no place to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She cannot even sit up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was suffering laying there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that laying position, just like buried alive, we heard shots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard young boys running, obviously Christian boys, running in excitement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We heard shooting because when they were rounding up the Jews, some tried to run away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some were sick in bed, invalids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- when they had the quota that they had-- let's say so many Jews that they had to have for that time to fill that train, that transport, there was a siren, like it's over.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people were able to come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we were afraid to come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What's going-- we stayed there until dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we lowered the ladder, and we came down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when my mother's turn came to come down, she fainted because the position she was laying and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when it was pitch dark, we had some friends that came at night, came to see us, and they give us a version of what took place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They told us who was taken away, who was shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's was a very depressing, gloomy perspective.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
